<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>غرف النوم والأطفال — زياد للتجارة</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans+Arabic:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="responsive-pro.css">
  <style>
    /* ── Categories Grid ── */
    .app-categories-grid { display: grid; gap: 16px; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr)); }
    .app-cat-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 20px 12px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; color: var(--ink); transition: var(--ease); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .app-cat-card:hover { border-color: var(--gold); box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft); transform: translateY(-2px); }

    /* ── Packages Grid ── */
    .pkg-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; padding: 0 var(--container-px); }
    .pkg-card { background: var(--surface-2); border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; display: flex; flex-direction: column; border: 1px solid var(--line); transition: var(--ease); }
    .pkg-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-lift); border-color: var(--olive); }
    .pkg-image { height: 200px; background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-color: #eee; }
    .pkg-content { padding: 32px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex: 1; }
    .pkg-content h3 { font-size: 1.4rem; margin: 0 0 8px; color: var(--ink); }
    .pkg-price { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .pkg-price strong { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--olive); }
    .pkg-features { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 32px; flex: 1; }
    .pkg-features li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .pkg-features li svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; stroke: var(--olive); }
    .btn-pkg { display: block; width: 100%; text-align: center; padding: 16px; background: #fff; color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--line); transition: var(--ease); }
    .btn-pkg:hover { background: var(--olive); color: #fff; border-color: var(--olive); }

    /* ── Split Hero (Bedrooms & Kids) ── */
    .hero-dual-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 24px var(--container-px);
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero-dual-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    .dual-card {
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 480px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 48px;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: var(--ease);
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }
    .dual-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.8) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.2) 60%, rgba(0,0,0,0.5) 100%);
      transition: var(--ease);
    }
    .dual-card:hover::before {
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.9) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.3) 60%, rgba(0,0,0,0.6) 100%);
    }
    .dual-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lift);
    }
    .dual-card-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .dual-card h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .dual-card p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      max-width: 320px;
    }
    .dual-card .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: var(--ease);
    }
    .dual-card:hover .btn {
      background: #fff;
    }
    .dual-card-features {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      padding-top: 20px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .dual-card-feature {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .dual-card-feature svg {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      stroke: var(--gold);
    }

    /* ── Image Category Cards ── */
    .image-categories-section {
      display: grid;
    }
    .img-cats-wrapper {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .img-cats-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
    }
    .img-cats-header h2 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .img-cats-header a {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .img-cats-grid {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      overflow-x: auto;
      padding-bottom: 16px;
      scrollbar-width: none;
    }
    .img-cats-grid::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
    .img-cat-card {
      min-width: 160px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--ink);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      transition: var(--ease);
    }
    .img-cat-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
    .img-cat-photo {
      width: 100%;
      height: 140px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: var(--surface-2);
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }
    .img-cat-card strong {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      display: block;
    }
    .img-cat-card small {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="shop-shell">
    <header class="top-note">
      <span>توصيل وتركيب مجاني داخل المدن الرئيسية</span>
      <span>ضمان 10 سنوات على الأخشاب والهياكل</span>
      <span>تصميم حسب ذوقك ومساحتك</span>
    </header>
    <nav class="main-nav" aria-label="التنقل الرئيسي"></nav>
    <main></main>
    <footer class="footer"></footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>